Privacy Policy for Al-Fath App

Bouzig Mustapha built the Al-Fath app as a free app. This SERVICE is provided by Bouzig Mustapha at no cost and is intended for use as is.

At Al-Fath, we are committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and disclose information when you use our app.

Information We Collect

We do not collect any personally identifiable information from you when you use our app. We do, however, require your permission to access your device's location to provide accurate salat times based on your location.

How We Use Your Information

The location data we collect is used solely to provide you with accurate salat times based on your location. We do not collect, store, or share any other information about you or your device.

Third-Party Services

We do not use any third-party services or analytics that collect data about you or your device.

Data Retention and Deletion

We do not store any data about you or your device. When you uninstall the app, all data related to the app is automatically deleted from your device.

Changes to This Policy

We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at mustapha.bzg@gmail.com.

Thank you for using the Al-Fath app developed by Bouzig Mustapha. We hope it helps you in your daily life and we value your trust in us.
